<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-fami=
ly:Consolas'>We
are glad to announce that a NEW EXERCISE will be proposed this year within =
the
Question Answering track at the Cross Language Evaluation Forum (CLEF). <o:=
p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-fami=
ly:Consolas'>For
more information and updates visit the new ResPubliQA website at:<o:p></o:p=
></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-fami=
ly:"Courier New"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal align=3Dcenter style=3D'text-align:center;text-autospa=
ce:none'><span
lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Consolas;color:blue'>htt=
p://celct.isti.cnr.it/ResPubliQA/index.php<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'text-autospace:none'><span lang=3DEN-US
style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:CMR10'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'text-align:justify'><span lang=3DEN-US
style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Consolas'>We invite participation, bo=
th
from academic institutions and industrial organizations, on this new task. =
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Consolas'>Guidelines des=
cribing
the task are distributed among the participants and are downloadable from t=
