ttp://celct.isti.cnr.it/ResPubliQA/Documents</span></a></span><span
lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Consolas;color:blue'><o:=
p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'text-align:justify;text-autospace:none'><span
lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-family:Consolas'>Training data </span><span lang=
=3DEN-US
style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Consolas'>have also been made availab=
