lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-family:Consolas'>participants in order to test t=
he
systems with procedures to be used in the formal evaluation campaign. </spa=
n><span
lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Consolas;color:blue'>htt=
p://celct.isti.cnr.it/ResPubliQA/Downloads</span><span
